name: Jzr R Mnl - Adele X Lionel Richie - Hello

content.text:
A mashed up by JZR R MNL

Capo on 1st fret

Verse:

   [ch]Am[/ch]    [ch]Am/G[/ch]           [ch]Am/F[/ch]                [ch]A[/ch]

       [ch]Am[/ch]  [ch]Am[/ch]
